[font=Times New Roman][size=4]
Installation for RaceMenu:
Extract the 'ellareal' files into Data/SKSE/Plugins/CharGen.
Then extract 'ellapreset.jslot' to Data/SKSE/Plugins/CharGen/Presets.
Open up the racemenu with the console command 'showracemenu'.
Select the Nord race.
Go into the presets tab and select 'ellapreset'.
Go to the sculpt tab and press import head, then select 'ellareal'.

Installation for ECE:
Extract '_27_commonTriraces.jslot' to Documents/My Games/Skyrim/CME_Save.
Open up the racemenu with the console command 'showracemenu'.
Select the Nord Race.
Go into the body tab and select slot load.
Load slot 27.
